title: “Rule 53,” Dak Prescott’s Injury, and a Rare Tuesday Night NFL Game | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Warren Sharp and Chris Vernon recap the Bill-Titans game and offer their biggest takeaways. They also discuss the impact schedule changes could have on teams, how much Dak Prescott is worth spread-wise, and league trends and characteristics they are seeing five weeks in.

Hosts: Warren Sharp and Chris Vernon
